column5: Well me and red devil headed out to the crappie zone for the day and man it was a slow slow day! Man that place is getting hit hard this year looks like a small lake simcoe lol!! We ended up getting some crappies for shore lunch but the highlight of the trip was the huge breakfast i made on the ice!! Bear sauage, bacon, home fries, eggs!! red devil couldint even eat it all he was so full ha ha ha! We had a great day out there will be doing it again soon.
Now that is a wholesome brekkie. Nothing like a good layer of bear grease to line the innards.  BTW, nice bag of fish.
mmmm looks yummy to me!!!!  I have heard it is busy there this year!  Cheers!
